kpi_info.title: DMCU fill factor calls
kpi_info.use: User plane resource usage exclusive for RNC object. It provides the highest resource usage value in the granularity period. The KPI value can also be interpreted as a call fill factor for the user plane resources: the remaining percentage is an indicator of how many more calls can be carried by RNC, assuming that the current proportions of different radio bearers remain the same. M615C1 for DSPPOOL_ID=RNC
